<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="es")

	meta(charset="UTF-8")
	meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1")
	title Cristaleria y Loza | Arias
	meta(name="description" content="Lo mejor en cristaleria y loza para tus banquetes.")
	link(rel="stylesheet", href="./css/main.css")
	link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.min.css")
body
	
	section(class="box-title-losaycristaleria")
	
	include ./menu/template.jade

	section(class="container")
		section(class="pru")
			article(class="row center")
				div(class="col-12 margintop5") 
					h1(class="title-section") Cristalería & Loza

			article(class="row left middle column")
				div(class="col-10")
					div(class="phon phon-x text-section") 
						p(class="parra") Nuestros servicio de Cristalería y Loza es muy completo pues tenemos:
						p(class="parra") <span class="subrayado negrita">Vasos, Copas, Platos, Salseras, Paneras, Cremeras y el plaque completo.</span>
						p(class="parra") Nos enorgullece decir que podemos cubrir eventos de hasta 2,000 personas.
						p(class="parra") Abajo encontraras información detallada sobre nuestros productos.
						p(class="parra") Este servicio viene incluida en algunos paquetes, así que no dudes en visitar nuestra sección de paquetes.
		

			article(class="row end middle")
				div(class="col-10")
					p(class="faq phon phon-x")
						a(href="faq.html" class="") Preguntas frecuentes 
						span(class="icon-question-circle")


			article(class="row center middle column margin3 box-style")
				div(class="col-12")
					div(class="text-section--sin_sombra")
						h2(class="title-deco") Cristalería

			
					div(class="tab_container")
						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab1" name="tabs" checked)
						label(for="tab1" class="label-tab")
							i(class="icon-drink")
							span(class="") Vasos

						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab2" name="tabs")
						label(for="tab2" class="label-tab")
							i(class="icon-cristaleria")
							span(class="") Copas

						section(id="content1" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Vaso común
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://www.como-limpiar.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/vasos_largos.jpg", alt="" class="img60")


						section(id="content2" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Copas
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://www.fideles.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/3-copas-.jpg", alt="" class="img60")
			

			article(class="row center middle column margin3 box-style")
				div(class="col-12")
					div(class="text-section--sin_sombra")
						h2(class="title-deco") Loza

					div(class="tab_container")
						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab3" name="tabsx" checked)
						label(for="tab3" class="label-tab--para_4")
							i(class="icon-rigurusidad")
							span(class="") Plato bajo

						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab4" name="tabsx")
						label(for="tab4" class="label-tab--para_4")
							i(class="icon-rigurusidad")
							span(class="") Plato llano

						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab5" name="tabsx")
						label(for="tab5" class="label-tab--para_4")
							i(class="icon-platos")
							span(class="") Plato hondo

						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab6" name="tabsx")
						label(for="tab6" class="label-tab--para_4")
							i(class="icon-salsera")
							span(class="") Salsero



						section(id="content3" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Usado como base en un banquete.
							p(class="parra") 
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://falabella.scene7.com/is/image/Falabella/3184083_1?$producto308$&iv=jYfn_2&wid=924&hei=924&fit=fit,1", alt="" class="img60")


						section(id="content4" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") El plato llano es donde es servido el plato fuerte.
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://publicdomainvectors.org/photos/plate.png", alt="" class="img60")
			

						section(id="content5" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Es comúnmente llamado sopero o cremero, pues se sirven en el este tipo de comidas.
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://www.veromatic.net/productos/ECV3100124%20plato%20sopero%2022%20oz.jpg", alt="" class="img60")


						section(id="content6" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Es útil para todo tipo de salsas que se sirven en un banquete.
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://shop.pordamsa.com/3919-home/elemental-plato-cuenco-20cm-6u.jpg", alt="" class="img60")
			

			article(class="row center middle column margin3 box-style")
				div(class="col-12")
					div(class="text-section--sin_sombra")
						h2(class="title-deco") Complementos

			
					div(class="tab_container")
						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab7" name="tabsy" checked)
						label(for="tab7" class="label-tab")
							i(class="icon-drink")
							span(class="") Plaque

						input(type="radio" class="tab" id="tab8" name="tabsy")
						label(for="tab8" class="label-tab")
							i(class="icon-cristaleria")
							span(class="") Cremera

						section(id="content7" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Plaque completo
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://i2.wp.com/www.laboratoriogastronomico.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/lg-slider-4.jpg?resize=610%2C300", alt="" class="img60")


						section(id="content8" class="tab-content")
							h3(class="color-grey center") Cremera, un elegante elemento para servir cremas.
							p(class="parra")
							figure(class="center")
								img(src="http://bylsa.com.mx/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/sopera-y-cucharon.jpg", alt="" class="img60")




			
			article(class="row center middle column margin3")
				div(class="phon col-6 end")
					button(class="button-contacto") Contacto
				div(class="phon col-6 start")
					button(class="button-green") Ver paquetes

	include ./footer/template.jade

	include ./derechos/template.jade		
		

	script(src="./js/bundle.js")
	script(src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js")
	script(class="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/modernizr/2.8.3/modernizr.min.js")
	script(src="./js/owl.carousel.min.js")
	script(src="./js/mains.js")